41 and control; appoint advisory committees as necessary; and enter into
42 contracts and do other things as necessary and incidental to the exercise of its
43 authority pursuant to this Article.
44 (8) Make recommendations concerning any matters within its purview pursuant
45 to this Article.
46 (9) Establish within the Office of the State Fire Marshal a marketplace pool of
